  "text": "Because our task required participants to view a CMC text message we measured fixation as steady gazes of 60 milliseconds. Studies show that people can read text with fixations as short as 50 to 60 ms [CITATION_1] . To collect fixation data we used a Tobii X120 eye-tracker. ",
